                  main PROC
;;;11133  //===============================================
;;;11134  int main (void) 
009f6a  b086              SUB      sp,sp,#0x18
;;;11135  {
;;;11136  char ind_reset_cnt=0;
;;;11137  //long i;

;;;11144

;;;11147  
;;;11148  
;;;11149  SysTick->LOAD = (SystemFrequency / 2000) - 1;
